-- Turkey's Akbank secures $1.36 bln syndicated loan 
-- By Seda Sezer
-- Thu Mar 20, 2014 03:23AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, March 20 (Reuters) - Turkish lender Akbank <AKBNK.IS> said on Thursday it had secured from international markets a one-year syndicated loan in two tranches of $221.8 million and 817.7 million euros ($1.14 billion).

